            <abstract>
                <p>Medico-magic prescriptions against various diseases (especially against female or gynaeocological diseases) as well as demons of
                    a similar type and content as those edited in <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/></bibl><!-- Add page numbers -->
                    and of a similar type as <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7544Prescr"/>, <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7545MedPres"/> 
                    and <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7546MedPrescr"/>, which are attested in the same manuscript 
                    (cf. <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient12034"/>).</p>
            </abstract>
